description:
Killer.Sharks.The.Attacks.Of.Black.December.x264-SM
                                                       
       Killer Sharks is a re-creation of the world-famous  
      attacks along the coast of Durbin, South Africa,   
      during the summer of 1957/1958.                   
                                                           
        Called "Black December", these attacks partly     
       inspired Peter Benchley's Jaws.
